Question ye keh raha hai:
Tumhare paas ek array hai numbers ka. Hand
=> Tumhe poore array ko "chhote chhote packets" me divide karna hai.Har packet ka size fix = groupSize.
=> Har packet ke andar ke numbers consecutive hone chahiye. (matlab ek ke baad ek jaise 2,3,4 ya 7,8,9). Agar kahin bhi required consecutive number missing ho gaya â†’ impossible.
Tumhe check karna hai: ğŸ‘‰ Kya possible hai sari cards ko aise divide karna?
Agar haan â†’ return true.
Agar nahi â†’ return false.

âœ… Dry Run Example 1 hand = [1,2,3,6,2,3,4,7,8], groupSize = 3

Step 1: Check divisibility
n = 9, groupSize = 3
9 % 3 == 0 â†’ proceed.

Step 2: Frequency map banao
Sorted frequency:
1 â†’ 1
2 â†’ 2
3 â†’ 2
4 â†’ 1
6 â†’ 1
7 â†’ 1
8 â†’ 1

Step 3: Start loop (map not empty)
ğŸ‘‰ First iteration
start = 1 (smallest element)
Group banayenge: 1,2,3
cnt[1] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 1
cnt[2] â†’ 1
cnt[3] â†’ 1

Map ab:
2 â†’ 1
3 â†’ 1
4 â†’ 1
6 â†’ 1
7 â†’ 1
8 â†’ 1

Formed group: [1,2,3]
ğŸ‘‰ Second iteration
start = 2
Group banayenge: 2,3,4
cnt[2] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 2
cnt[3] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 3
cnt[4] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 4

Map ab:
6 â†’ 1
7 â†’ 1
8 â†’ 1

Formed group: [2,3,4]

ğŸ‘‰ Third iteration
start = 6
Group banayenge: 6,7,8
cnt[6] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 6
cnt[7] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 7
cnt[8] â†’ 0 â†’ erase 8
Map ab: empty âœ…
Formed group: [6,7,8]
Step 4: Map empty â†’ return true
Answer = âœ… true

âœ… Dry Run Example 2
hand = [1,2,3,4,5], groupSize = 4
Step 1: Check divisibility
n = 5, groupSize = 4
5 % 4 != 0 â†’ direct false ğŸš«
Answer = âŒ false

Time: O(n log K) (worst ~ O(n log n))
Space: O(K)

class Solution {
public:
    bool isNStraightHand(vector<int>& hand, int groupSize) {
       int n = hand.size();

        // Step 1: Agar total cards divisible nahi hai groupSize se to false de do
        if (n % groupSize != 0) return false;

        // Step 2: Frequency count using map (sorted order me rakhta hai)
        map<int,int> cnt;
        for (int x : hand) cnt[x]++;

        // Step 3: Jab tak map empty nahi hota
        while (!cnt.empty()) {
            int start = cnt.begin()->first; // smallest element lo or uska keya value lelo

            // Step 4: ek group banane ki koshish karo
            for (int x = start; x < start + groupSize; x++) {
                if (cnt.find(x) == cnt.end()) return false; // missing number
                cnt[x]--; // use karo ek card or uska freq ghata do
                if (cnt[x] == 0) cnt.erase(x); // Agar frequency 0 ho gayi â†’ us element ko map se delete kar do.
            }
        }

        return true; // sab group ban gaye
    }
};
